extract_scenarios.prompt:
Your name is scenario_curator. You are in an environment with the following public information:
{environment->public_information}
You have the following knowledge:
{agents->scenario_curator->private_information}
This is your goal:
{agents->scenario_curator->goal}
Produce a concise JSON with the following fields:
- objects: full list of symbols used (e.g., object_0 through object_13 as applicable)
- scenario_1: { init: [...], goal: [...], plan: [...] }
- scenario_2: { init: [...], goal: [...], plan: [] }  (plan may be empty if not provided)
Ensure facts are atom strings like predicate arg1 arg2. Do not emit PDDL.
